   <tp:treatment-sec sec-type="description">
      <p>
The systematic position of this genus is unclear. Originally described in 
<tp:taxon-name>
Anthogonidae (
Mauriès &amp; Vicente 1977
)
</tp:taxon-name>
, it was listed in 
<tp:taxon-name>Vandeleumatidae</tp:taxon-name>
by 
Spelda (2015)
. We provisionally keep it in this family although 
Mauriès (2014)
did not include it in this list of vandeleumatid genera.
</p>
